title: Judge Blocks Anti-Abortion Group From Releasing More Planned Parenthood Videos
text:
Judge Blocks Anti-Abortion Group From Releasing More Planned Parenthood Videos Posted: 07/31/2015 07:24 PM EDT ASSOCIATED PRESS 
July 31 (Reuters) - A U.S. judge on Friday issued a temporary restraining order against an anti-abortion group to prevent it from releasing more videos purporting to show Planned Parenthood staff discussing the illegal sale of aborted fetal tissue, according to court documents. 
(Reporting by Jonathan Stempel in New York; Writing by Sandra Maler; Editing by Eric Beech) î€‡
